The '''9j ion power cell''' was the backup power source in the [[Cygnus Spaceworks/Legends|Cygnus Spaceworks]] [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Assault Gunboat]], and was manufactured by [[Iotek]]. Eventually Iotek found an alternate backup power source that was more sustainable, which they converted most of their ships to use.

